Customer_Groups
    [Documentation] Checks that new customer group could be added
    Log into Zed
    Open Customer Groups screen
    Click Add new Customer Group
    Fill Name, Description
    On Customers tab select 2 customers
    Click Save
    Check that message shown 'Customer group was created successfully.'
    Click View and assert name, description, customers
    Click Edit Customer Group
    Update Name
    Uncheck 1 selected customer
    Add new customer that wasn't selected before
    Click Save
    Assert name and list of customers